11
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:26,760
Yilin.

12
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:28,760
Your mother

13
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:31,570
has been gone for so many years now.

14
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:32,880
I, your father,

15
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,200
