24
00:01:59,000 --> 00:01:59,600
Coming.

25
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:04,880
Let's go.

26
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,280
Starting a new life.

27
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:22,100
What do I have to start a new life with?

28
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:46,920
Hello?

29
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:48,079
Ms. Mu Yilin, hello.

30
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,520
This is Yuanding Cemetery in Khorgos.

31
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,160
Your mother Pearl's grave in Khorgos

32
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,890
